text: Denis Jančo (born 1 August 1997) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for FC ŠTK 1914 Šamorín as a midfielder. ==Club career== ===FK AS Trenčín=== Jančo made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for AS Trenčín on 30 May 2015 against ViOn Zlaté Moravce entering in as a substitute in place of Ryan Koolwijk.ZLATÉ MORAVCE VS.
